{"tid":853183,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有睇遺書、公開","createTime":"2018-10-08T11:53:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T05:13:16.000Z","uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b2863c9a3632ee9bb9c04a097312bf019da66657","tid":853183,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T11:53:39.000Z","msg":"感覺似日本初中版13 reasons why<br />\n女主一開波自殺<br />\n全班同學一人收到一封遺書<br />\n開班會傾返自殺原因嚟互相傷害<br />\n每個公開都會黑化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但暫時推理都幾小兒科下<br />\n仲有同班序列上下層矛盾<br />\n男豬睇落仲係outsider"},{"pid":"2e6a2e85c4c2a61406172f255c3489c8ac0a6288","tid":853183,"uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T12:05:28.000Z","msg":"另外想求群像劇題材推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇標題講嘅角色或者主角從來冇出現過嘅作品？<br />\n即係聽說桐島退社了咁樣<br />\n配角群羅生門式咁以各自視角去拼湊完整故仔<br />\n風陵夜話咁靠口耳相傳塑造返個唔在場嘅主角出嚟<br />\n或者似成田良悟咁一集轉一個敍事者多線並行<br />\n想搵啲靠配角群衝突去主導劇情嘅作品嚟睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde6e0f9b2187c4398f9f76b213bdb73ff604ded","tid":853183,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T22:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af81e201162842a204a7a1cad7ae9da79d60c8f3","tid":853183,"uid":9034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:37:06.000Z","msg":"我最新睇到嗰集個第二名扮完野扮到俾人踢爆<br />\n<br />\n廢到<br />\n<br />\n仲要俾人踢爆完就顏偽<br />\n但明明冇實際戰功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇朋友遊戲算啦樓主"},{"pid":"3c8309c08416ed808b44be4aa742469a3ff500e6","tid":853183,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af81e201162842a204a7a1cad7ae9da79d60c8f3","tid":853183,"uid":9034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T03:37:06.000Z","msg":"我最新睇到嗰集個第二名扮完野扮到俾人踢爆<br />\n<br />\n廢到<br />\n<br />\n仲要俾人踢爆完就顏偽<br />\n但明明冇實際戰功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal